{"type":null,"faqId":37053,"title":"手环充满电大概需要多长时间？如何充电？支持多大电流？是不是只支持USB充电？","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\r\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\r\n.s1{font-family:Times New Roman;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<div class=\"detail_c_1 fl mt1\">\n<div style=\"POSITION: relative; PADDING-LEFT: 5%; PADDING-RIGHT: 5%\" id=\"softwareDescription\" class=\"column fl\" jQuery171004321040704821466=\"16\">\n<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">手环充满电大概需要<span>1.5</span>个小时。您可以根据手环屏幕上的电池图标动态来判断充电情况。充满后电池图标显示常亮。</span></p>\n<p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">充电电压电流可以是<span>5V 0.5A</span>、<span>5V 1A</span>、<span>5V 1.5A</span>、<span>5V 2A</span>。</span></p>\n<span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">常见的手机<span>USB</span>充电器、车载<span>USB</span>接口、充电宝<span>USB</span>接口都可以为手环充电。同时也支持电脑的<span>USB</span>口对<span>B2</span>进行充电。<span>B2</span>支持自动限流，建议使用<span>2A</span>以内的充电器，</span><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">请勿长时间使用高出规格的充电器充电</span><span style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: line; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt\">，同时提醒您充电时保证充电口干燥。</span> </div>\n<!--\n<div id=\"floatDiv\"></div>\n--></div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":204,"faqType":"电池&充电&功耗","useful":9,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2217","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Battery-Charging-Consumption","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750140000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":687,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,充电时间,充电器,充电,USB充电,电流,电压,手环不能充电,不充电,充不饱电","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}